sub_title: GIS Intern | MSc in Remote Sensing / Geo-Information Science | BSc in Geophysics / Geology
summary:
I am a recent graduate from the University of Twente majoring Geo-Information Science and specializing in Applied Remote Sensing. 
I graduated from a double degree program between the "University of Strasbourg" and "Azerbaijan State Oil and Industry University" with a BSc in Geoscience.

Passionate about Energy Transition and have been able to participate in several activities & projects related to sustainable energy development. 

My enthusiasm for interesting work is boundless and I am highly motivated to constantly develop my skills and grow professionally. I am confident in my ability to take over challenges, improve quickly, and my strong work ethic, ability, and passion would make me a valuable asset to every team I work.
